title: [2001] The Album (FLAC) [Since I Left You - Zomba Promo]
description:
This is the rare UK promo version of The Avalanches' "Since I Left You" album, which was just called 'The Album'.

This is the complete unedited album. Contains every sample intact and the rare track "With My Baby"

In FLAC format, individual tracks with ReplayGain metadata, cue and EAC log
